OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FHe is a legend by definition, a man
OL,7,Fwith a never-say-die attitude and a
OL,8,Fcareer that was fearless from the
OL,9,Fstart.
OL,11,FThat start began back when Nigel
OL,12,FMansell was just six years old, living
OL,13,Fin Hall Green in Birmingham.
OL,15,FBefore 1959, Nigel had a little bike,
OL,16,Fand he was trying to be an engineer
OL,17,Fand saw someone with handlebars that
OL,18,Fwere the wrong way and he used a
OL,19,Fspanner to turn them the other way.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FAs he rode it away, at his first turn
OL,7,Fthe handlebars turned the other way
OL,8,Fbut the wheel didn't, so he fell off
OL,9,Fin front of a bus.
OL,11,FA police officer spotted him and
OL,12,Fwalked him home - that is when he
OL,13,Fthought he needed to learn more about
OL,14,Fengineering.
OL,16,FBut, it was his father, Eric, who
OL,17,Finspired Nigel to get behind the
OL,18,Fwheel. He worked for Lucas Aerospace
OL,19,Fand bought him a one-wheel kart and
OL,20,FNigel never looked back.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FNigel karted all the way up to the age
OL,7,Fof 20, then he moved onto single-
OL,8,Fseaters and Formula Ford. In 1976, he
OL,9,Fhad his first Formula Ford race.
OL,11,FFast forward and Nigel was making his
OL,12,Fdebut in Formula 1, but it was a
OL,13,Fpainful one as he was getting burnt
OL,14,Fwhile sitting in the car on the grid
OL,15,Fbecause the fuel tank was leaking into
OL,16,Fthe cockpit at the 1980 Austrian Grand
OL,17,FPrix.
OL,19,FBut after that, he never looked back.
OL,20,FOne of the best ways to describe Nigel
OL,21,Fis humble.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FHe was teammates with some of the best
OL,7,Fdrivers to grace the sport, with his
OL,8,Ffavourites being Riccardo Patrese and
OL,9,FKeke Rosberg, and his not-so-
OL,10,Ffavourites being Alain Prost, Mario
OL,11,FAndretti and Nelson Piquet.
OL,13,FIn his own words, he didn't know he
OL,14,F"could beat his teammate".
OL,16,FBut he was extremely determined,
OL,17,Fsometimes aggressive, but always
OL,18,Fdaring, which made him one of the
OL,19,Fexciting drivers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FSomeone who saw that talent within
OL,7,FNigel was the great Colin Chapman. He
OL,8,Fgave Nigel the chance to try out with
OL,9,FLotus.
OL,11,FWhen he spoke about Colin, you could
OL,12,Finstantly tell how much he meant to
OL,13,FNigel. He was like a father figure to
OL,14,Fhim.
OL,16,FGiving him some of the best advice of
OL,17,Fhis career and life. It wasn't just
OL,18,Fthe advice he gave to Nigel, but his
OL,19,Factions too.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FNigel said he remembers when he
OL,7,Fqualified third with Lotus, and Colin
OL,8,Fasked him why he wasn't happy. Nigel
OL,9,Freplied that he was, but it would've
OL,10,Fbeen more lovely if his wife,
OL,11,FRoseanne, were with him.
OL,13,FColin asked why she wasn't there, and
OL,14,FNigel said that he couldn't afford for
OL,15,Fher to be there.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FHe was paid #25,000 for his contract,
OL,7,Fbut had to pay for his own hotels,
OL,8,Fairfares and car hire, and his wife
OL,9,Fwas working to subsidise him. So,
OL,10,FColin decided to double his wage that
OL,11,Fweek, so Roseanne could retire and be
OL,12,Fwith him at certain races.
OL,14,FA year later, Nigel didn't qualify for
OL,15,Fthe British Grand Prix as the car was
OL,16,Fbanned; he was crestfallen. Nigel said
OL,17,Fthey were going through a tough time
OL,18,Fin his personal life.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FThey were renting a semi-detached
OL,7,Fplace, and people kept knocking on the
OL,8,Fdoor asking for autographs because
OL,9,Fthey lived close to the street.
OL,11,FNigel felt they were getting harassed,
OL,12,Fand they couldn't get a mortgage
OL,13,Fbecause he didn't earn enough. So,
OL,14,FColin gave him a cheque worth #70,000,
OL,15,Fso he could move.
OL,17,FNigel said that when Colin passed away
OL,18,Fso early in their relationship in
OL,19,F1982, "it was like the arms had just
OL,20,Fbeen chopped off your body."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FTwo-years-later he moved onto Williams
OL,7,Fand started to upset the applecart by
OL,8,Fwinning races, but he was getting an
OL,9,Funwanted record.
OL,11,FThe former Formula 1 driver Stirling
OL,12,FMoss told Nigel that he was the driver
OL,13,Fwith most wins to never win the
OL,14,Fchampionship. So, Nigel decided to
OL,15,Fgive it back to him.
OL,17,FIn 1992, Nigel managed to fulfil the
OL,18,Fdream of a boy from Birmingham by
OL,19,Fwinning the Formula 1 Drivers' World
OL,20,FChampionship.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FBut, he felt like he'd become the
OL,7,Fpeople's champion years before. Oh,
OL,8,Fand he also managed to give that
OL,9,Funwanted record back to Stirling Moss.
OL,11,FHis driving career was littered with
OL,12,Frecords and triumphs including
OL,13,Fbecoming the last driver to be
OL,14,Fpersonally selected by the great Enzo
OL,15,FFerrari to represent The Prancing
OL,16,FHorse.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FSomething which he is immensely proud
OL,7,Fof, and he knows what it means to make
OL,8,Fthe Tifosi proud. They even called him
OL,9,Ftheir moustachioed British hero 'Il
OL,10,FLeone' (The Lion).
OL,12,FHe believes the seven-time world
OL,13,Fchampion Lewis Hamilton will do as
OL,14,Fwell. His message to Lewis is to hang
OL,15,Fon in there, and he will get it.
OL,17,FOne of the most iconic moments from
OL,18,FNigel's career was when he gave a lift
OL,19,Fto the Brazilian driver Ayrton Senna.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FSenna's car had broken down, so Nigel
OL,7,Fdecided to pick him up. Despite the
OL,8,Fefforts of a steward, they both drove
OL,9,Foff.
OL,11,FMansell also went off to IndyCar
OL,12,Fracing in America, where he
OL,13,Fimmediately dominated, even on the
OL,14,Funfamiliar high-speed ovals, and
OL,15,Fbecame the 1993 IndyCar champion.
OL,17,FIn 1995, Nigel hung up his helmet and
OL,18,Fleft the sport he loved for good.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FNow, after gaining so much, he wants
OL,7,Fto give back. Nigel has done a number
OL,8,Fof charitable works. Including working
OL,9,Fwith UK Youth.
OL,11,FIt's a charity with a vision that all
OL,12,Fyoung people are equipped to thrive
OL,13,Fand empowered to contribute at every
OL,14,Fstage of their lives.
OL,16,FNigel's involvement with the charity
OL,17,Fdates back to the 1990s, when it ran a
OL,18,Fprogramme to teach young people about
OL,19,Fcars, including safe driving practices.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,FSince he became president in 1999, he
OL,7,Fhas worked tirelessly to support and
OL,8,Fpromote the charity.
OL,10,FSo, what bit of advice does Nigel have
OL,11,Ffor the next generation?
OL,13,FNigel said: "The advice I would give,
OL,14,Fregardless of what sort of background
OL,15,Fyou come from, is sometimes you only
OL,16,Fhave one or two opportunities, don't
OL,17,Fdrop the ball.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777313467
OL,3,CThe life of a lion: Nigel Mansell on
OL,4,Chow he conquered the world
OL,6,F"When you get the opportunity...if you
OL,7,Fprepare yourself, programme your mind
OL,8,Fand make sure you know what is going
OL,9,Fto come at you, so whatever comes at
OL,10,Fyou, you're ready for it...just be
OL,11,Fprepared, look at every angle, no
OL,12,Fsurprises, you know you can do a good
OL,13,Fjob, do the good job, it will be
OL,14,Fnoticed."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/15
